Package edu.cs2430.assignment3

Class Student

java.lang.Object
edu.cs2430.assignment3.Student
public class Student extends Object
A class to represent a student

A student will have an array of at most 5 possible schedules.
The student will automatically be assigned the next available student id in the constructor. This id is stored and maintained in nextStudentId.
